Source.Comments: This Source is a self-reference. It represents the database and the query that produced the xml document. The sourceID contains a timestamp. The full URL is given in the tag UniformResourceIdentifier but you need to unescape ampersands and angle brackets to re-use it. Query was: select * where (RadTransWavelength >= 5000.0 AND RadTransWavelength <= 5010.0) AND ((AtomSymbol = 'Fe'))
